content.rendered:
Directed by Rohit Raj Goyal

Written by Rohit Raj Goyal. Abhishek Manoharchanda. Gaurav Srivastav

Star Tushar Pandey(Titu). Deepika Singh(Mosmi). Raghuvir Yadav(Shukla Ji). Sapna Sand(Prabhavati Shukla Ji). Veerendra Saxena(Narendra Trivedi (as Virendra Saxena)). Samta Sagar(Sugandha Trivedi). Brijendra Kala(Sajan Chaturvedi)

Language Hindi

Producers Mahendra Vijaydan Detha. Dinesh Kumar

Production Altair Media. Sabal Production
